FBIS3-19504 "drweu053_a_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-053 Document Type:Daily Report 17 Mar 1994 AUSTRIA Christa Krammer Appointed New Health Minister AU1703124694 Vienna ORF Teletext in German 1204 GMT 17 Mar 94 AU1703124694 Vienna ORF Teletext Language: German Article Type:BFN [Text] Burgenland Provincial Councilor Christa Krammer (49) is the new health minister. Shortly after her presentation by Chancellor Vranitzky she was sworn in by President Klestil. Krammer is a lawyer. As provincial councilor she was responsible for, among other things, the field of preventive health care. She told the press conference introducing her that she considers all spheres of her ministry (health, consumer protection, sports) equal. The Nationalrat is currently holding a debate on the government reshuffle.
